result.execSummary:
The defendant Alecia Michelle Clifton was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Alecia Michelle Clifton is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Alecia Michelle Clifton was found guilty of Bail Jumping-Felony, a class H felony, Wisconsin Statutes 946.49(1)(b).
  • Alecia Michelle Clifton was found guilty of Possess w/Intent-Cocaine (>1-5g), a class F felony, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(1m)(cm)1r.
